Lives, n.;

Defn: pl. of Life.

LOAVES
Loaves, n.;

Defn: pl. of Loaf.

LOWBRED
Low"bred`, a.

Defn: Bred, or like one bred, in a low condition of life;
characteristic or indicative of such breeding; rude; impolite;
vulgar; as, a lowbred fellow; a lowbred remark.
